Vaccine Rollout in San Francisco Neighborhoods:
The Reported Percent Vaccinated, The Estimated Percent Eligible,
And The Difference Between The Two
Data reflects the percent of residents in a neighborhood who have received at least
one dose of the vaccine as of March 16th, 2021 according to data.sfgov.org
and the estimated percent of residents who are eligible according to CDPH guidelines.
